title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland Auditorium Arena on 1979-12-28
lineage: Master Cassettes (Nakamichi DR-1)> Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6 MHz) > dBpoweramp 24/96 > Adobe Audition CC 2019 > TLH flac2496
description:
Set I
Sugaree
Mama Tried >
Mexicali Blues
Row Jimmy
It's All Over Now

Set II

Playing In The Band >
Drums >
Space >
Uncle John's Band >
I Need A Miracle >
Bertha >
Good Lovin'

Encore:
Casey Jones
One More Saturday Night


Comment

Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
